  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of Ciprofloxacin for
      Inhalation in the treatment of patients with non-cystic fibrosis (CF) bronchiectasis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
